When setting up this project for the user or wiring integrations
(Supabase/Stripe/Meta/PostHog/Foreplay), follow the interview flow and hard
rules in AGENTS.md at the repo root. Key points: never commit .env or any
key; SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY never reaches the browser or deploy env; Supabase
"allow signups" stays OFF; every integration is optional - only wire what the
user actually has. Human docs: README.md and docs/SETUP.md.
